<DocsLayout title="Introduction">
  <h2>Welcome to Rep-li-bot</h2>
  <p>
    Rep-li-bot is a local-first desktop application that enables anyone to build private apps
    and widgets using plain English descriptions, powered by AI code generation.
  </p>

  <h3>Key Features</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>No Code Required</strong> - Describe what you want in plain English</li>
    <li><strong>Local & Private</strong> - All data stays on your machine</li>
    <li><strong>AI-Powered</strong> - Uses OpenAI-compatible APIs for code generation</li>
    <li><strong>Theme Customization</strong> - Four built-in themes to choose from</li>
    <li><strong>Secure Runtime</strong> - Sandboxed preview with permission boundaries</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Quick Navigation</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="/docs/installation">Installation</a> - Get Rep-li-bot installed on your Windows PC</li>
    <li><a href="/docs/getting-started">Quick Start</a> - Build your first app in minutes</li>
    <li><a href="/docs/ai-configuration">AI Configuration</a> - Set up your AI provider</li>
    <li><a href="/docs/usage">Creating Projects</a> - Learn how to use the builder</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>System Requirements</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Windows 10 or later (64-bit)</li>
    <li>4 GB RAM minimum</li>
    <li>200 MB free disk space</li>
    <li>Internet connection (for AI features)</li>
  </ul>
</DocsLayout>
